Happy Friendship Day! Don’t forget to wake up your friends early while Travelling. Watch till the end for pictures😍❤️

It’s always a good idea to wake up early and go to these famous places otherwise it gets insanely crowded! There was a km long queue here after we were done. 

📍Fushimi Inari Shrine in Kyoto, Japan is absolutely beautiful. I’ve seen so many pictures of this place and I finally made it to this dreamy place ❤️
